data.description: Welcome Home to this 3 bedroom/2.5 Bath home in Award Winning Westfield-Washington Schools! Conveniently located in Sandpiper Lakes on the border of Westfield and Noblesville. Centrally located to all things Westfield including Grand Park, Grand Junction Plaza and the Monon & Midland Trails. This home has New Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring on Main Floor and upstairs bathrooms, New Roof & Gutters 2021 & New Windows 2022. Relax in your Private Backyard Oasis offering a Custom Brick Patio surrounded by Beautiful Mature Trees. You won't find that with new construction. The Kitchen and Living Room have Vaulted Ceilings, creating an Open & Airy space. The possibilities are endless!  **Seller is offering a $1,200 carpeting credit at closing.
